{
  "id": "f25bace8baf7480a8af91ceea74d5936",
  "title": "Book Maker - Advanced Text Layout & Animation Tool",
  "description": "Easily generate a whole book from a block of text. Can also be used for advanced text layouts & animation.",
  "longDescription": "<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/OIml5a0S9Ok\" rel=\"nofollow\">Book Maker Demo</a></p><p><br /></p><p>If you&#39;re looking for a tool to help with wrapping text, laying out blocks of text in a grid or layers, or you simply want to generate a book or flip book from a block of text, this is the tool for you! By default, BP_Bookmaker lays pages out in a stack, with a cover page on top. But you can customize the materials, the way the &#39;pages&#39; are laid out, and much much more to really do just about ANYTHING with a text render actor.</p><p><br /></p><p>This tool is a direct extension of <a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/aa23daf520d64eb6ab005e7c4501d324\" rel=\"nofollow\">Page Maker</a>, if you just need a single page with animation capabilities, and the formatting/wrapping options, Page Maker might be the better tool for you!</p>",
  "technicalDetails": "<p>Features:</p><ul><li> Easy to use</li><li> Plug and Play</li><li> Versatile</li></ul><p>Number of Blueprints: 1 main blueprint (BP_Bookmaker) &#43; demo game mode and pawn &#43; everything from  <a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/aa23daf520d64eb6ab005e7c4501d324\" rel=\"nofollow\">Page Maker</a>.</p><p>Input: Keyboard, Mouse, Gamepad</p><p>Network Replicated: No</p><p>Supported Development Platforms:</p><p>\tWindows: Yes</p><p>\tMac: Yes</p><p>Documentation: <a href=\"https://youtu.be/OIml5a0S9Ok\" rel=\"nofollow\">Book Maker Demo</a></p><p>Important/Additional Notes: This tool is a direct extension of my <a href=\"https://www.unrealengine.com/marketplace/en-US/product/aa23daf520d64eb6ab005e7c4501d324\" rel=\"nofollow\">Page Maker</a> tool, available for only $7.99</p>",
